                "content": {
                  "text": "- **Agentic workflow**: `apps/playground/docs/AGENT_STARTING_TEMPLATE.md`\n- **CDP bridge details**: `apps/playground/docs/AGENTIC_FEEDBACK_LOOPS.md`\n- **Testing strategy**: `packages/expo-audio-studio/docs/TESTING_STRATEGY.md`",
